This is a generic OJS plugin tested for OJS 2.3.6

Install
======= 

Install as usualy generic plugin

Configuration
=============

the issueCarousel can work with custom custom images per issue or with the OJS cover image.

the custom covers may complain the follow criteria:
 - Directory: the generic cover path (p.e. public/journals/1/covers/)
 - file name: Volume-Number-locale.png (p.e. 98-2-es_ES.png)
 if custom cover not found /covers/default.png will be displayed

Use
===

to include the carousel to your OJS include the carousel hook call to your template where you want to print it, as follow:

 {call_hook name="Templates::Index::issueCarousel"}


